⁣I FORGIVE my rapist.⠀
⠀
Why? NOT because his actions are forgive-able..⠀
⠀
I forgive him because he got to take SO much from me. He doesn’t get to take anything else, especially not my peace of mind.⠀
⠀
I will NEVER know how HE sleeps at night⠀
But I forgive him, I have moved on the best I can.⠀
And I sleep just fine. ❤️
Excerpt from the newest episode of She’d Be Proud. 🦋 Dress is @revolve #revolveme

The fact that you have come to this spot in your life and to have the courage that you have proves, that you are an amazingly strong person. You continuously spread the encouragement that things will get better but also are not afraid of showing a side of you where you don’t try to hide what is actually happening. It is absolutely amazing Lindsay! Please don’t stop spreading the light on the things that you do! I love you so so so much and thank you for being my role model! ❤️❤️❤️
So proud of you! 🦋Your an incredibly strong women! 💪🏻💪🏻
